<div><head>《去伐論》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1384_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1384_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1384_CHANT_001-1a.2">夫君者必量才任以授官，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1384_CHANT_001-1a.3">參善惡以毀譽，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1384_CHANT_001-1a.4">課功過以賞罰者也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1384_CHANT_001-1a.5">苟伐其善必忘其惡，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1384_CHANT_001-1a.6">於是怨責之情必存乎心，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1384_CHANT_001-1a.7">希望之氣必形乎色，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1384_CHANT_001-1a.8">此矜伐之士、自賢之人所以為薄，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1384_CHANT_001-1a.9">而先王甚惡之者也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1384_CHANT_001-1a.10">君子則不然，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1384_CHANT_001-1a.11">勞而不伐，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1384_CHANT_001-1a.12">施而不德，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1384_CHANT_001-1a.13">致恭以存其位，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1384_CHANT_001-1a.14">下人不隱其功，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1384_CHANT_001-1a.15">處不避汙，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1384_CHANT_001-1a.16">官不辭卑，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1384_CHANT_001-1a.17">唯懼不任，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1384_CHANT_001-1a.18">唯患弗能。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1384_CHANT_001-1a.19">故力有餘而智不屈，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1384_CHANT_001-1a.20">遠咎悔而行成名立也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1384_CHANT_001-1a.21">歐陽詢《藝文類聚》卷二十三。<lb/></seg>
</p>
